column5: Drlee,I sent you a private message,but received no response. Can you tell me where in Fond du Lac Wis you purchase your salted/frozen minnows. I will be in Sturgeon Bay visiting my cousin and would like to buy some minnows to take on a Canadian fly-in trip at end of June Thank You in advance Larry S
For some reason did not get the pm. Dutch's Trading Post, 258 North Main Street, 920-922-0311. Ask for "Rick." Let me know if you need follow up. Doc Lee
